quran[12{c,v,t}:
67,1,"nihayat buzurag o bartar hai woh jis ke haath mein kaayenaat ki saltanat hai, aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
67,2,"jis ne mout aur zindagi ko ijaad kya taakay tum logon ko aazma kar dekhe tum mein se kon behtar amal karne wala hai, aur woh zabardast bhi hai aur dar guzar frmane wala bhi"
67,3,"jis ne teh Bar teh saat aasman banaye tum Rehman ki takhleeq mein kisi qisam ki be-rabti nah pao ge phir palat kar dekho, kahin tumhe koi khlal nazar aata hai ?"
67,4,baar baar nigah دوڑاؤ tumhari nigah thak kar namuraad palat aeye gi
67,5,hum ne tumahray qareeb ke aasman ko azeem al shan charaghoon se aaraasta kya hai aur unhen shyatin ko maar bhaganay ka zareya bana diya hai inn shaitano ke liye bharakti hui aag hum ne muhayya kar rakhi hai
67,6,jin logon ne apne rab se kufar kya un ke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur woh bohat hi bura thikana hai
67,7,jab woh uss mein phainky jayen ge to uskay dharnay ki holnaak aawaz sunen ge aur woh josh kha rahi hogi
67,8,"shiddat ghazab se phati jati ho gi har baar jab koi anbwah is mein dala jaye ga, uss ke karnde unn logon se poucheen ge"" kya tumahray paas koi khabardaar karne wala nahi aaya tha? """
67,9,"woh jawab den ge"" haan, khabardaar karne wala hamaray paas aaya tha, magar hum ne usay jhutla diya aur kaha Allah ne kuch bhi nazil nahi kya hai, tum barri gumraahi mein parre hue ho """
67,10,"aur woh kahin ge"" kash hum suntay ya samajte to aaj iss bharakti hui aag ke saza vaaru mein nah shaamil hotay """
67,11,"is terhan woh apne qasoor ka khud aitraaf kar len ge, laanat hai un dozakhiyon par"
67,12,"jo log be dekhe apne rab se drtay hain, yaqeenan unn ke liye mughfirat hai aur bara ajar"
